description:
Willie "The Lion" Smith in concert in Paris on 29 November 1965 at the L'Ecole Normale de Musique. The recording was apparently broadcast over French TV on 13 March 1966.
For the complete 23-minute broadcast on DVD please message me.
title: Willie "The Lion" Smith - Paris 1965
